    Incredibly spacious 5 bedrooms, 4 bathroom, 2-story with a 2-car detached garage, pool, spa, and a nice brick curb appeal! Inside you'll find a grand foyer, beautiful hardwoods and tile downstairs, high ceilings, updated paint, two staircases, plantation shutters, a formal dining, crown molding, formal living with a fireplace, breakfast room, and lots of built-ins. The den also has a fireplace and is adjacent to the kitchen that boasts a huge island, granite countertops, recessed lighting, ample cabinet space, and a lovely backsplash. Downstairs also holds the master suite with dual sinks, a garden tub, and separate shower while upstairs includes the large game room, French door study/5th bedroom, extra room, and the secondary bedrooms. This home is located on a large cul-de-sac lot with no neighbors to the west and Green Trails amenities just a couple minutes away!

      Coming Soon

      Coming Soon listings are homes that will soon be on the market. The listing agent for these homes has added a Coming Soon note to alert buyers in advance. Learn more about coming soon listings.

      Foreclosures

      These properties are currently listed for sale. They are owned by a bank or a lender who took ownership through foreclosure proceedings. These are also known as bank-owned or real estate owned (REO).

      Foreclosed

      These properties are owned by a bank or a lender who took ownership through foreclosure proceedings. They may soon be listed for sale. These properties are not found on a multiple listing service (MLS).

      Pre-Foreclosures

      The lender initiated foreclosure proceedings on these properties because the owner(s) were in default on their loan obligations. Pre-foreclosures also include properties for which a foreclosure auction is scheduled. These properties are not found on a multiple listing service (MLS).

      Pending & Under Contract

      Sellers of these homes have accepted a buyer's offer; however, the home has not closed.
